   Hello everybody, especially to all them Fluffy/MAXs SysOps! :-] You
   all, or most of you know me and what I get up to in my docs so I'll
   try not to bore you with silly comments/docs, but I know u love it!

   This MAXs door, U2S (Upload 2 SysOp) is nothing  special or new, so
   I don't care what you think, or whether u use it or not, so there!?
   And I don't care what that wanker Paul of Shoikan Grove (..or Greg)
   may think (..I think they're gay), but go fuck yaself's u dikheads!

   It simply allows users to upload private files to the SysOp. Wow..!

   Just @{" install " link run} and run the door and see for yaself! ..Fucking easy!


@endnode
@node run " U2S - by Glen Martin of GREMLiNS BBS"
 @{"°°" link grems}
      _   _   ___   ___ 
     | | | | |_  ) / __|   @{"°"} @{" Install "} @{"°°"} @{"°"}
     | |_| |  / /  \__ \
      \___/  /___| |___/   @{b}(c) 1998 GREMLiNS MAXsWARE plus NSA & LSD@{ub}


   Lets go! U unpack the archive (already done obviously shithead) and
   then u create a "new directory" called "gremlins" in your doors dir
   wich is easy.  I've decided and to meet requests from sum SysOps, I
   am now placing all my doors (old updates and new) into a "main" dir
   called "gremlins" so to keep it all tidy, etc and keep all my doors
   together, for some reason.. Okay!? So fuck u if u don't like this?!

   Okie dokie, follow these simple (?) steps:

   o You  must put an  "assign" command in  your startup  sequence and
     this is, eg: assign gremlins: bbs:doors/gremlins .

   o Create a directory 'U2S' in your main files: path.

   o Move the "U2S dir" and  files inside into the "gremlins dir"  and
     run it from there via MAXs, eg: gremlins:u2s/u2s .

   o When door is run, "U2S.ans1" is  shown, and if [i]=Info  selected
     will show "U2S.nfo". "U2S.ans2" is shown when a user has uploaded
     a file(s) explaining what to do now, eg: leave msg, etc.

   You, hopefully, should get it working and know wat to do from here.
   Any probs, u know who to @{" contact " link call}, okie dokie!? ;-}


@endnode
@node rego " U2S - by Glen Martin of GREMLiNS BBS"
 @{"°°" link grems}
