      \___/  /___| |___/   @{b}(c) 1998 GREMLiNS MAXsWARE plus NSA & LSD@{ub}


   The door, "U2S", defaults to  show the Registered User  as me when
   [i]=Info selected! So if you want it rego'd in your name, just ask
   me,  call me or email me such a request...  or simply complete the
   "My Version" rego form  included in this archive.   Read this form
   for more information on what "My Version" all means, etc. Yipee..!

   The reason I do this is to know how much interest there are in all
   my MAXs doors I do, from the rego responses, comments and emails!


@endnode
